fields.description:
Indexes for the bugtracker application could not be created by syncdb. 

Error message:

django.db.utils.DatabaseError: (1005, "Can't create table 'ahernp_dmcm.#sql-5d91_bec33c' (errno: 150)")
fields.title: Bugtracker Indexes

fields.update_text: This is a known problem (see https://code.djangoproject.com/ticket/18256) when you have a mix of MySQL tables are using the different storage engines (i.e. MyISM and InnoDB). The default used to be MyISM and changed to InnoDB.
